snippet.title: Century 21 Films
snippet.description: The work of Century 21 Films spans drama to documentary, miniature effects to puppet shows. Clients include BBC, ITV, Mammoth Screen, Halifax and others. Their latest project, 'Nebula-75', is a Supermarionation puppet drama produced during lockdown.
